      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, cut <strong>half</strong> your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>into wedges and dice the <strong>remaining onion</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
