    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and your <strong>ground paprika</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until softened</p>",
