    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the diced onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and<strong> onion wedges </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until slightly softened</p><p>Increase the heat to high and<strong> </strong>add all the <strong>chopped mushrooms </strong>to the pan with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Cook for 5-6 min or until the mushrooms have softened</p>",
