    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [250ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> with your <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> and <strong>Henderson's Relish </strong>– this is your <strong>stock</strong></p><p>Once the mushrooms have softened, add 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp] </span><strong>flour </strong>to the pan and stir everything together</p><p>Add the <strong>stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until slightly thickened</p>",
